Antenna.
Ten segmented and filiform; 1,390 µm long, 0.77 of total body length. Scape 68 µm long, with 4 setae. Pedicel 68 µm long, with 4 or 5 setae. Lengths of segments III–X (µm): III, 207; IV, 170; V, 156; VI, 165; VII, 156; VIII, 161; IX, 141; X, 97. Approximate number of setae on each of segments III–X: 
III 25–27
