VIII 24
or 25; 
IX 19–21
; 
X 11
or 12; VIII and IX with 1 ventral antennal bristle, X with 2 subapical antennal bristles and 2 or 3 subapical sensilla basiconica; capitate, apically knobbed sensory setae absent.
